The paper focuses on developing a deep learning recommendation model for personalization and recommendation tasks, which involves handling categorical features. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG), Information Retrieval (cs.IR), and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper discusses the implementation of the model in PyTorch and Caffe2 frameworks, which suggests that it may also belong to the Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS) and Databases (cs.DB) sub-categories.
